THE CHOSEN ONES brings together 16 favorite tracks from Aussie group The Black Sorrows including "Come On Come On" and "The Crack Up."

1993 greatest hits compilation from Joe Camilleri, the man behind the Black Sorrows, one of Australia's most talented artists. 16 tracks including cover versions of Van Morrison's 'Brown Eyed Girl' & Bob Marley's 'Stir It Up'.

If you are a fan of heart felt, rock and blue with a reggae flavour, do yourself a favour and grab a taste of The Black Sorrows.
